"tid":1169693,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"715534cd9a7a46d676b78bd7871b87e613f0dfec","tid":1169693,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T16:28:03.000Z","msg":"up乜春<br />\n拎呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T17:00:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小A最近總是做同一個夢，夢裡一個陌生男人對她說：「你來嘛，你來找我嘛，我等你&hellip;&hellip;」夢中的小A總不回答。<br />\n<br />\n每次醒來想起夢，小A都覺得很荒誕，那天她想，要是再夢見他，就和他說說話吧，看他想怎樣。<br />\n<br />\n又一個晚上，小A又夢見那個男的在呼喚她，她就問：「你是誰？我怎麼才能找到你呢？」<br />\n<br />\n男人就說：「明天中午12點在公園門口的站台上來找我吧，我這裡有一顆痣。」男人用手指著自己的下巴。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n於是，小A匆匆找了好友，讓好友陪她一起去。<br />\n<br />\n第二天中午12點，兩人在約定的地方等，卻不見男人來。天氣炎熱，小A就對好友說：「太熱了，我到對面買兩支雪糕，你在這裡等我。」說完，小A就過街去了。<br />\n<br />\n就在這時，一輛車子沖了過來，路中間傳來一聲慘叫&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n好友跑過去一看，小A已倒在血泊中。她抬頭想找人幫忙把小A送醫院，才發現肇事的是一輛靈車，司機已經下了車，面色蒼白地站在小A旁邊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n打開的車門，車上的玻璃棺材中躺著一個下巴有個黑痣的男人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T17:09:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />笑話？"},"cited